{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#[[Category:Christianity]] The act of [[excommunicate|excommunicating]] or [[eject|ejecting]]; especially an ecclesiastical censure whereby the person against whom it is pronounced is, for the time, cast out of the communication of the church; exclusion from fellowship in things spiritual.

